		<br />
	</div><br />I've tried the Channel Mixer tool, but if I try and take away the red, it just looks really green, and then if I try and take away the green, the image just turns dark. I then tried to up the brightness, and then it looked really washed out, and then the saturation, and the colors were still off.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_confused.gif" alt=":?" title="Confused" /> I don't know if anyone has any advice, but I figured this is the most technically minded place on the internet I'm on.<br /><br />Edit: It occurred to me that I should probably have both pictures in two separate files for others' convenience.

		

