		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm getting kinda okay results with Curves, adjusting blue and red mostly.  You get more control than with Levels (and you can use a Levels setting as a starting point for curve adjustment).  It's still hard to get everything to look right at the same time, though - getting the green screen perfect makes certain foreground features look too blue - or maybe I just don't know what I'm doing?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
